rows.label: tlk70000006_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Yeah, so we were meant to be going
to your award ceremony, but thanks
to Teeco, we were late!

rows.label: tlk70000006_04_msg0002
rows.name:
She said she couldn't decide what
to wear. I just don't understand
how her mind works sometimes.

rows.label: tlk70000006_04_msg0003
rows.name:
She promised we'd get there
early and get a decent seat
too... Fat chance!

rows.label: tlk70000006_04_msg0004
rows.name:
I mean, it's a knighting ceremony. You
don't see one of those everyday! Who
knows when they'll have another?
